name: AF-201 Auto Filter
details:
Sensitivity: determines when the effect will trigger.
Peak: boosts the center frequency for more dramatic filtering (like a Resonance control on a synthesizer).
Filter (LP/BP/HP): Selects the type of filter: Lowpass, Bandpass or Highpass.
Drive (Up/Down): Selects the direction of the filter sweep: upwards or downwards.
Range (High/Low): Selects the frequency range of the filter.
